13 4–3106.
14 (A) (1) WHEN A QUALIFIED COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT ENTITY OBTAINS
15 APPROVAL OF AN APPLICATION AND A DESIGNATION OF A QUALIFIED EQUITY
